  {
    "text": "I think this is one of the more",
    "start": 206.172,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "expensive endorsements",
    "start": 207.574,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "that Andrew Cuomo",
    "start": 208.808,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "has ever gotten",
    "start": 209.409,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "because it took $959",
    "start": 209.976,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "million in tax breaks",
    "start": 211.377,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "that he gave Elon Musk",
    "start": 213.112,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "for Elon Musk's",
    "start": 214.28,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "pet projects back",
    "start": 214.948,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "when Cuomo was the governor.",
    "start": 215.715,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're seeing",
    "start": 216.95,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "the two twin architects",
    "start": 218.051,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "of this second term of it,",
    "start": 220.286,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Donald Trump's presidency",
    "start": 221.821,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "in the president himself",
    "start": 222.855,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "and Elon",
    "start": 224.123,
    "duration": 0.468
  },
  {
    "text": "Musk saying",
    "start": 224.591,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "clearly to New Yorkers",
    "start": 225.491,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "that their candidate",
    "start": 226.626,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "is Andrew Cuomo,",
    "start": 227.86,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "and they picked Andrew Cuomo",
    "start": 228.828,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "because they know",
    "start": 230.163,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "that he will be the puppet",
    "start": 231.097,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "that they want right here",
    "start": 232.098,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "in New York City.",
    "start": 233.166,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "And he's showing himself",
    "start": 234.0,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "to not just be that,",
    "start": 234.867,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "but also to be their parrot",
    "start": 235.501,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "in the language",
    "start": 236.603,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "that he's using",
    "start": 237.27,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "to close out this election.",
    "start": 237.737,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay,",
    "start": 238.605,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "you talk about billionaires,",
    "start": 239.672,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "and there have been",
    "start": 241.14,
    "duration": 0.568
  },
