    "text": "some really wealthy",
    "start": 241.708,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "individuals who have come out",
    "start": 242.809,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "and put money in attacks",
    "start": 244.077,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "against you in recent days.",
    "start": 245.979,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "Right.",
    "start": 247.113,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Former Mayor",
    "start": 247.78,
    "duration": 0.434
  },
  {
    "text": "Michael Bloomberg among them.",
    "start": 248.214,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "There are plenty",
    "start": 249.482,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "of other business leaders",
    "start": 250.016,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "who, in private,",
    "start": 251.117,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "will have are afraid.",
    "start": 252.785,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "They have concern.",
    "start": 254.387,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "There are very few",
    "start": 255.355,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "who actually",
    "start": 256.322,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll talk about it publicly,",
    "start": 256.789,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "but one of them is Jamie Dimon",
    "start": 257.824,
    "duration": 1.701
  },
  {
    "text": "from JP Morgan.",
    "start": 259.525,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm thinking about this",
    "start": 260.426,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "in light of Trump",
    "start": 262.061,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "calling you a communist.",
    "start": 262.662,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Jamie Dimon did not call",
    "start": 263.997,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "you communists. He was more,",
    "start": 264.897,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "intellectual about it.",
    "start": 267.567,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "He said,",
    "start": 268.501,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "what does he really think?",
    "start": 269.168,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "You know,",
    "start": 270.47,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "he was",
    "start": 271.17,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "part of that socialist",
    "start": 271.671,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "democratic thing,",
    "start": 273.206,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "which literally is more Marxist",
    "start": 273.873,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "than socialist.",
    "start": 275.675,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "And I read it,",
    "start": 276.876,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "but I don't know",
    "start": 277.51,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "what he believes in that.",
    "start": 278.678,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 280.146,
    "duration": 0.267
  },
  {
    "text": "So this is basically",
    "start": 280.413,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "saying he's",
    "start": 281.08,
    "duration": 0.267
  },
  {
    "text": "not really sure",
    "start": 281.347,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "where you stand on things.",
    "start": 281.914,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "But what do you say",
    "start": 284.484,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "to that concern?",
    "start": 285.451,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "Is Marxist",
    "start": 286.352,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "something you're comfortable",
    "start": 287.654,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "with?",
    "start": 288.988,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I am a",
    "start": 289.489,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "democratic socialist.",
    "start": 290.156,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "And I've said it",
    "start": 291.124,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "time and again,",
    "start": 291.591,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "when was that",
    "start": 292.191,
    "duration": 0.468
  },
  {
    "text": "quote from, from Jamie",
    "start": 292.659,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Diamond from",
    "start": 293.826,
    "duration": 0.668
  },
  {
    "text": "from Jamie Diamond.",
    "start": 294.494,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "It was from fortune last week.",
    "start": 295.695,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay.",
    "start": 297.63,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "A fortune conference last week",
    "start": 298.197,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "because what he's also come out",
    "start": 299.432,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "and said in public",
    "start": 300.733,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "is that in our success",
    "start": 301.734,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "this is something",
    "start": 303.603,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "that business leaders",
    "start": 304.27,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "would also hope for,",
    "start": 305.071,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "for the success of the city.",
    "start": 305.905,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "And I put that forward",
    "start": 307.24,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "to say that despite",
    "start": 308.174,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "where New Yorkers may stand",
    "start": 309.042,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "on my candidacy,",
    "start": 310.643,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "whatever qualms they may have,",
    "start": 311.978,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "they know that I'm",
    "start": 313.379,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "actually being honest",
    "start": 313.98,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "with them about my ideas",
    "start": 314.847,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "about who",
    "start": 316.082,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm looking to fight for.",
    "start": 316.382,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's sadly",
    "start": 317.45,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "unique in this race,",
    "start": 318.251,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "because what you have",
    "start": 319.752,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "is someone in Andrew Cuomo",
    "start": 320.586,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "who spent the entirety",
    "start": 322.221,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "of a primary campaign",
    "start": 323.523,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "on the premise",
    "start": 324.791,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "that he was the best suited",
    "start": 325.458,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "to take on Donald Trump.",
    "start": 326.626,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "And here we are",
    "start": 327.994,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "with the Kiran",
    "start": 328.928,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "that Donald Trump",
    "start": 329.762,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "is endorsing Andrew Cuomo. So.",
    "start": 330.63,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "So let me ask you,",
    "start": 332.298,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "because that was October 17th.",
    "start": 332.832,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "So it was actually a week",
    "start": 334.133,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "and a half ago.",
    "start": 334.867,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "But I want to ask you,",
    "start": 335.368,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "because you asked me",
    "start": 336.235,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "when when he said that,",
    "start": 336.836,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "are you talking to him?",
    "start": 339.739,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "Are people like that, people",
    "start": 340.873,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "that you're going to sit down",
    "start": 342.041,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "with and,",
    "start": 342.875,
    "duration": 0.434
  },
  {
    "text": "and eagerly work with or not?",
    "start": 343.309,
    "duration": 3.103
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, I'll have conversations",
    "start": 346.412,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "with anyone.",
    "start": 347.613,
    "duration": 0.434
  },
  {
    "text": "And I've spoken to",
    "start": 348.047,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "Jamie Diamond briefly,",
    "start": 349.248,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "and I've spoken to a number",
    "start": 350.316,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "of other business leaders",
    "start": 351.417,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "across the city",
    "start": 352.585,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "about my proposals.",
    "start": 353.619,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "I know that",
    "start": 355.021,
    "duration": 0.334
  },
  {
    "text": "there are disagreements",
    "start": 355.355,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "around my fiscal policy,",
    "start": 356.089,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "that I think",
    "start": 357.123,
    "duration": 0.334
  },
  {
    "text": "we should raise",
    "start": 357.457,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "income taxes on.",
    "start": 358.057,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "The top",
    "start": 358.791,
    "duration": 0.267
  },
  {
    "text": "1% of New Yorkers",
    "start": 359.058,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "who make $1 million",
    "start": 360.093,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "or more a year by 2%,",
    "start": 361.227,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "or the fact",
    "start": 362.428,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "that I think corporations",
    "start": 363.162,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "top tax rate should be matching",
    "start": 364.063,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "that what they pay",
    "start": 365.998,
    "duration": 0.735
  },
  {
    "text": "in new Jersey.",
    "start": 366.733,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "And still",
    "start": 367.633,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "there is room for an immense",
    "start": 368.334,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "amount of agreement",
    "start": 369.602,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "on what it means",
    "start": 370.47,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "to bring the city forward.",
    "start": 371.17,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'll always leave that",
    "start": 372.305,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "door open.",
    "start": 373.239,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "So, okay,",
    "start": 374.307,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "so let me just ask",
    "start": 375.241,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "you about President Obama.",
    "start": 376.342,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "I know",
    "start": 377.71,
    "duration": 0.434
  },
  {
    "text": "that you had a",
    "start": 378.144,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "conversation with him.",
    "start": 378.811,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "What was that",
    "start": 381.18,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "conversation about",
    "start": 382.315,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "your most recent one?",
    "start": 383.75,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "I appreciate it.",
    "start": 384.751,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "The conversation",
    "start": 385.752,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "with President Obama",
    "start": 386.386,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "and we spoke about both",
    "start": 387.12,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "the near post headline is",
    "start": 388.454,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "that he's not endorsing it.",
    "start": 389.756,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 391.257,
    "duration": 0.334
  },
  {
    "text": "Well,",
    "start": 391.591,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "the New York Post",
    "start": 392.325,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "has a lot of fun",
    "start": 392.892,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "with their headlines, to put it",
    "start": 393.393,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "put it lightly.",
    "start": 394.293,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "It was a conversation",
    "start": 395.995,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "where we were",
    "start": 396.896,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "speaking about the importance",
    "start": 397.196,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "of hope in politics,",
    "start": 398.131,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "the delivery",
    "start": 399.165,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "of that kind of an agenda.",
    "start": 400.066,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "And I also shared with him",
    "start": 401.3,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "that the remarks",
    "start": 402.568,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "that I had shared",
    "start": 403.269,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "outside of a mosque",
    "start": 405.037,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Bronx",
    "start": 406.272,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "not too long ago",
    "start": 407.273,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "was inspired in part",
    "start": 408.474,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "by his remarks on race",
    "start": 409.575,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "of a more perfect union",
    "start": 411.21,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "many years ago.",
    "start": 412.278,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "And I think there is often",
    "start": 413.246,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "a tendency",
    "start": 414.48,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "in our politics",
    "start": 415.248,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "to think solely in",
    "start": 416.048,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "a 24 hour news cycle",
    "start": 416.916,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "and the need to",
    "start": 418.418,
    "duration": 0.633
  },
  {
    "text": "sometimes step back",
    "start": 419.051,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "and speak",
    "start": 420.052,
    "duration": 0.334
  },
  {
    "text": "to the soul of a city.",
    "start": 420.386,
